  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/Rvq8Ow69CYVib32MDsJl9KmJf3hrB9mX2ibOt0BiazjaXP41BQWzYdrOr2JD4uJWsTkMric37uibWhaJrthKG5iawR7gSEbnnUKsagAcIDTGg2jjk/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"505195776\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4d1f49e6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FRvq8Ow69CYVib32MDsJl9KmJf3hrB9mX2ibOt0BiazjaXP41BQWzYdrOr2JD4uJWsTkMric37uibWhaJrthKG5iawR7gSEbnnUKsagAcIDTGg2jjk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; width: 100%;\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">2026数学界直接寄了！顶尖学者未能推进的证明被跑通，连菲尔兹奖得主也被指出论文逻辑瑕疵。当AI智能体能自主接管真理的验证权时，现有的科研范式还能维持多久？</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">太离谱了！数学界被</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em; margin-top: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI Gauss洗劫</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em; margin-top: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">了</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">仅5天，它就啃完了人类15月都啃不动的硬骨头。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Viazovska 8维+24维球填充证明，硬转成20万行Lean代码，90倍效率碾压！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"316\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"371\" data-imgfileid=\"505195769\" data-ratio=\"0.5621212121212121\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"660\" data-width=\"660\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fa52c9ff&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYUCWAcgB3tKG6TvRzz9t8ZBhqKukmszjssWI2YFXbfZMPlNu29Pw4wIFmicV0ic2LueSmicUYyzd1Rpley4AMric9YcnGXnJv3TeII%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人类精英 VS AI？纯属算盘怼量子，根本打不过。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">网友吐槽：救命，这AI卷疯了，DeepMind都得认怂？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Gauss给菲尔兹奖主发「纠错邮件」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">8维和24维的证明针对的是球体堆积问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在n维欧几里得空间中，如何将相同大小的球（无重叠）尽可能密集地排列，并证明特定格子达到最优。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"505\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505195780\" data-ratio=\"0.8739352640545145\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1174\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=00364dc9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYWWy6Hvc5bCcUiaKWRGgLkWd9djam1K52oVHI3FurWwdGwia85IY9P6KnZfevMGLepdIbQ0ia7uZGz9wxtKI471etW3Cy2GFWibK2M%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个问题已有数百年历史。在大多数维度难以严格证明最优，但8维和24维是特殊维度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2022 Viazovska靠8维E8+24维Leech晶格球填充爆杀全场，成第二位女菲奖得主。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3083941605839416\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1096\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1096\" data-height=\"338\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"173\" data-imgfileid=\"505195766\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=87640526&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYXDvuibfWvcNIKorgygFROT24T6c7m11jI49pibr2s8XaayNv7FjwIFkZwuCI8ibavjEo9F0EWn2BElvHlQOsRszfs7jaKKjnXia6Y%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文传送门：<a href=\"http://arxiv.org/abs/1603.04246\" target=\"_blank\">http://arxiv.org/abs/1603.04246</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"151\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"308\" data-imgfileid=\"505195768\" data-ratio=\"0.2692307692307692\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1144\" data-width=\"1144\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bad024f0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYV3jnTKS5grGhonyAWLWbCAlCic6VAdGR4I3XDTn7DiaDFrnALMkenFQ0LbOaKibQdp24GZWgd6UndT7VV8zUJ9bhLqvEAGVerUlY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文传送门：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1603.06518\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/1603.06518</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但现在，AI卷上来了！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Viazovska的论文有几十页，人类逻辑压缩成自然语。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但电脑眼里，「理应如此」这种词根本不能理解。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在Gauss介入之前，一个团队耗时15个月，试图将这一菲尔兹奖成果进行Lean形式化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但受制于人类认知带宽的限制与注意力衰减，工程推进缓慢。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从15个月到5天，人类处理超大规模逻辑链条的算力已经触达上限。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">8维证明形式化：AI狠戳菲奖论文瑕疵</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Gauss底层是推理智能体闭环，碾压老代码。检索模块狂扫千篇文献补背景，重构模块直转Lean代码+实时编译验证。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3831223628691983\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2370\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2370\" data-height=\"908\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"215\" data-imgfileid=\"505195767\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=39b372ef&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYXg1O3pNfeW5tcJOzmq8ALI5vWIPM80myc5tkibxoB9k5lCu9nfvDWnwJZBCjMUul7maibEV733bJVPTwWcJdu6KHKxbhCdiaMXMc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">处理Viazovska 8维E8模系数时，Gauss发现了30个逻辑瑕疵。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在Lean社区中，这些尚未被机器验证的步骤通常被标注为「sorry」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而对于人类开发者而言，填补这些「sorry」意味着需要查阅巨量的文献，并将其翻译成机器能识别的语法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">转折点出现在论文第14页的一处不等式推导。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Gauss在连续执行4096次推理步进后，反馈了编译错误，并指向了原论文中的一处排版与微观逻辑瑕疵。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在没有人类干预的情况下，Gauss通过自主搜寻历史定理库，重构了这一步的边界条件，并补全了这段缺失的证明。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在此之前，人类数学家始终作为逻辑的主理人，AI仅负责执行；而现在，Gauss展现出了比人类更敏锐的纠错直觉。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于学界而言，8维证明的完全形式化本身就是一个分水岭。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它不仅产出了数万行高质量的Lean代码，更证明了推理智能体具备识别并修复人类逻辑盲点的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种能力将数学验证从模糊地带，推向了100%可运行的数字绝对值。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">24维证明：零蓝图自主重构</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在数学界，24维空间的Leech Lattice远比8维的E8晶格复杂。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Gauss这一次没有任何预设的蓝图可以参考，其复杂程度显著高于8维情况。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在8维证明的形式化过程中，人类团队已经提前在Lean社区搭建了脚手架，标注了大量的「sorry」作为导向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但在24维证明中，Gauss面对的是一片逻辑真空。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">24维球体填充证明的难点在于，它深度耦合了关于Leech晶格唯一性的复杂群论证明。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Gauss展现出的核心突破是无蓝图推理。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在证明Leech晶格是24维空间中唯一能够实现最大密度的结构时，Gauss表现出了超强的文献综合能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3413940256045519\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1406\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1406\" data-height=\"480\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"192\" data-imgfileid=\"505195765\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5fc85c37&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYUBFyib6ribqhlSxyPDfg4J3Kib0YCONNLmwzBJlstqiaiahzasZ7jsQN2XvEXickoq29I78Cqgzic9shDS9tdKWhLbLvR5gd1HykRTKs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文传送门：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.04567\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.04567</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">系统通过其检索模块，定位了数十篇跨越30年的关联论文。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它理解了Viazovska原始论文的逻辑主线，通过跨文献比对，自行识别出需要引入的外部引理，例如关于Co0康威群的对称性特征。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在24维证明的深度推进中，Gauss需要生成并验证超过12万行的Lean代码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这一规模下，任何由于上下文理解偏差导致的逻辑漂移，都会引发指数级的报错崩溃。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Gauss通过推理链条都监控，实时计算每一个推论步骤的置信度。当置信度低于阈值时，它会触发回溯机制，重新检索数学公理库。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在24维证明的第2048个逻辑块中，Gauss独立补全了拉普拉斯算子在特定流形上的谱隙估计。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43434343434343436\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1188\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1188\" data-height=\"516\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"244\" data-imgfileid=\"505195770\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d7660f08&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYVTxGxekBXiarpWJXFDEm9ltHmOicpQDWMM9x5tE7IvkV8cBHVsVXydLSFUdwDJt77E5RPWibpNCCVJIY46rQ6hFJI7CibfY9Tz258%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一步在原论文中被视为「显而易见」的结论，但在形式化验证中，它需要近万行的证明代码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Gauss仅用14小时就完成了这段逻辑的填补。AI对高难度智力活动的重塑，变成了全流程科研链条的自主接管。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在逻辑验证的竞技场上，人类已经不再不可或缺。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">范式转移：数学证明的工程化纪元</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">长期以来，数学证明的传播媒介是自然语言论文。这种媒介形式虽然灵活，却伴随着极高的理解门槛与逻辑验证成本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Gauss的出现，标志着数学正从自然语言文学转向可运行的软件工程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Math,Inc.首席执行官Jesse Han将这一转变比作计算机科学从打孔纸带时代进入高级语言时代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9126712328767124\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1168\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1168\" data-height=\"1066\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"513\" data-imgfileid=\"505195771\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=15f7ab7e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYVkdJSHCsOGWOjHqqfGpqzr5e4guPGBkPeTr0pnf6EWTjdtJEueTgawdWyLxzH1IHzPCosHJ6nJ2rYmjh4vvQwwkNiazZy5fRY0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在打孔纸带时代，程序员需要关注每一个底层的物理比特；而在高级语言时代，开发者得以站在抽象层级上构思复杂的系统逻辑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Jesse Han认为：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种技术的最终结果将是解放数学家……让他们去梦想新的数学世界。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">未来数学家将转向更高的架构设计，数学证明等工作将由类似Gauss的推理智能体自动完成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">数学作为所有自然科学的底层语言，其工程化进度的加快，将直接传导至密码学、量子计算、航天轨道计算等强逻辑领域。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这种新范式下，人类将作为指挥家，繁重的演绎推理则交给具备ASI潜力的智能体。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Maryna Viazovska曾被视为人类智力的巅峰，如今它已转化为服务器中202000行的比特。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这个真理不再需要人类中介的时代，我们是否有勇气沿着AI开辟的路径，去触碰那些超越人类直觉的未知疆域？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://spectrum.ieee.org/ai-proof-verification?share_id=9202657&amp;utm_campaign=RebelMouse&amp;utm_content=IEEE+Spectrum&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter\" target=\"_blank\">https://spectrum.ieee.org/ai-proof-verification?share_id=9202657&amp;utm_campaign=RebelMouse&amp;utm_content=IEEE+Spectrum&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter</a></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://x.com/mathematics_inc/status/2028542388717986135?s=20\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/mathematics_inc/status/2028542388717986135?s=20</a></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
